  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load all knowledge files. Read the repo JSON `projects/spaarke-daily-update-service/notes/playbooks/daily-briefing-narrate.json`.</step>
    <step order="2">Verify pre-conditions via MCP `read_query`: confirm `sprk_analysisaction` rows for `BRIEF-NARRATE-TLDR`, `BRIEF-NARRATE-CHANNEL`, `BRIEF-VALIDATE-ENTITY-NAMES` exist in spaarkedev1 and are Active.</step>
