    <step order="4">Deploy: invoke `mcp__dataverse__create_record` (or `update_record` if upserting) with payload: sprk_playbookcode = "BRIEF-NARRATE", sprk_playbooktype = 0, sprk_playbookmode = 1, sprk_triggertype = 0, sprk_capabilities = 100000006, sprk_configjson = JSON-serialized configjson from repo file, statecode = 0 (Active), statuscode = 1 (Active default).</step>
    <step order="5">Verify deployment: MCP `read_query` to fetch the deployed row + check sprk_configjson byte/semantic match with repo file.</step>
    <step order="6">Run `jps-playbook-audit` skill against `BRIEF-NARRATE`. Confirm clean output.</step>
    <step order="7">Capture evidence in `notes/deployments/011-narrate-playbook-deploy.md`: deployed row ID, audit output, sample read_query result.</step>
    <step order="8">Update TASK-INDEX.md: change this task's status to &#x2705;.</step>
    <step order="9">If deviations from plan, document in projects/spaarke-daily-update-service-r4/notes/.</step>
